entries.transmission_start: \#pcontrast3 CorSec Command: < \#pcontrast1 Stay in the area as you relay the hyperspace activity back to us.  More Raiders are on their way so be ready. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.transmission_received: \#pcontrast3 CorSec Command: < \#pcontrast1 The data has been sent! \#pcontrast3 >
entries.trans_update: \#pcontrast3 CorSec Command: < \#pcontrast1 Captain! You have to win this mission. Be careful and keep an eye out for attack! \#pcontrast3 >
entries.title_d: Survive the retributive assault from the Evil Raiders
entries.title: Endor System: Survive the Evil Raider Assault
entries.split_quest_alert: \#pcontrast3 CorSec Command: < Good work, Captain. We are tracking one or more Tyrants not far from your location.  Try to disable one and recover any information that may help us with our pirate hunting. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.quest_reachpoint_d: Large hyperspace surges detected in this area
entries.outofrange_failed: Mission Failure! Objective out of range! Return to your superior for further instructions.
entries.outofrange: Tactical Computer: < Warning! Warning! Objective too far away! Warning! Warning! >
entries.mission_complete: Mission Success! Continue with further objectives.
entries.found_loc: \#pcontrast3 CorSec Command: <  \#pcontrast1 Okay. We've detected suspicious activity in Sector H-910. Go check it out and report back to us. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.first_attack: \#pcontrast3 CorSec Command: < \#pcontrast1 Enemy ships coming in weapons armed.  We're counting on you, Captain \#pcontrast3 >
entries.attack_stopped: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Hostile activities have ceased \#pcontrast3 >
entries.attack_notify: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Enemy craft detected on attack vector \#pcontrast3 >
entries.arrived_at_loc: \#pcontrast3 CorSec Command: < \#pcontrast1 This really doesn't look good. I suspect enemy ships to show up at any moment. Keep an eye out. \#pcontrast3 >
